{"id":332,"ayahs":[{"number":1,"arabic":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ ٱتَّقُوا۟ رَبَّكُمْ ۚ إِنَّ زَلْزَلَةَ ٱلسَّاعَةِ شَىْءٌ عَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"O men! Be conscious of your Sustainer: for, verily the violent convulsion of the Last Hour will be an awesome thing!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2596.mp3","surahId":22,"words":[{"id":347,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":348,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسُ","translation":"মানবজাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":349,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱتَّقُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা ভয় করো","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":350,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبَّكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের রবকে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":352,"position":5,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":353,"position":6,"arabic":"زَلْزَلَةَ","translation":"প্রকম্পন","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":354,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلسَّاعَةِ","translation":"ক্বিয়ামাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":355,"position":8,"arabic":"شَىْءٌ","translation":"ব্যাপার","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":356,"position":9,"arabic":"عَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"ভয়ংকর","audioUrl":"wbw/022_001_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":357,"position":10,"arabic":"١","translation":"(১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَ تَرَوْنَهَا تَذْهَلُ كُلُّ مُرْضِعَةٍ عَمَّآ أَرْضَعَتْ وَتَضَعُ كُلُّ ذَاتِ حَمْلٍ حَمْلَهَا وَتَرَى ٱلنَّاسَ سُكَٰرَىٰ وَمَا هُم بِسُكَٰرَىٰ وَلَٰكِنَّ عَذَابَ ٱللَّهِ شَدِيدٌۭ","translation":"On the Day when you behold it, every woman that feeds a child at her breast will utterly forget her nursling, and every woman heavy with child will bring forth her burden [before her time]; and it will seem to thee that all mankind is drunk, although they will not be drunk - but vehement will be [their dread of] God’s chastisement.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2597.mp3","surahId":22,"words":[{"id":1425,"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"যেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1426,"position":2,"arabic":"تَرَوْنَهَا","translation":"তা তোমরা দেখবে (সেদিন)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1427,"position":3,"arabic":"تَذْهَلُ","translation":"বিস্মৃত হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1428,"position":4,"arabic":"كُلُّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1429,"position":5,"arabic":"مُرْضِعَةٍ","translation":"স্তন্যদাত্রী (মা)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1430,"position":6,"arabic":"عَمَّآ","translation":"তাহ'তে যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1431,"position":7,"arabic":"أَرْضَعَتْ","translation":"সে দুধপান করিয়েছে (অর্থাৎ দুগ্ধপোষ্যকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1432,"position":8,"arabic":"وَتَضَعُ","translation":"ও গর্ভপাত করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1433,"position":9,"arabic":"كُلُّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1434,"position":10,"arabic":"ذَاتِ","translation":"সম্পন্ন","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1435,"position":11,"arabic":"حَمْلٍ","translation":"গর্ভ (গর্ভবতী)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1436,"position":12,"arabic":"حَمْلَهَا","translation":"তার গর্ভকে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1437,"position":13,"arabic":"وَتَرَى","translation":"এবং দেখবে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1438,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسَ","translation":"লোকদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1439,"position":15,"arabic":"سُكَـٰرَىٰ","translation":"মাতালের মতো","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1440,"position":16,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"অথচ না","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1441,"position":17,"arabic":"هُم","translation":"তারা (হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1442,"position":18,"arabic":"بِسُكَـٰرَىٰ","translation":"মাতাল","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1443,"position":19,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنَّ","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1444,"position":20,"arabic":"عَذَابَ","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1445,"position":21,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌র","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1446,"position":22,"arabic":"شَدِيدٌۭ","translation":"কঠিন (শাস্তি)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_002_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1447,"position":23,"arabic":"٢","translation":"(২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":3,"arabic":"وَمِنَ ٱلنَّاسِ مَن يُجَٰدِلُ فِى ٱللَّهِ بِغَيْرِ عِلْمٍۢ وَيَتَّبِعُ كُلَّ شَيْطَٰنٍۢ مَّرِيدٍۢ","translation":"And yet, among men there is many a one who argues about God without having any knowledge [of Him], and follows every rebellious satanic force","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2598.mp3","surahId":22,"words":[{"id":2480,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","translation":"আর কেউ কেউ (মধ্য হ'তে)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2481,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسِ","translation":"মানুষের","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2482,"position":3,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2483,"position":4,"arabic":"يُجَـٰدِلُ","translation":"(যারা) বিতর্ক করে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2484,"position":5,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"সম্বন্ধে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2485,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2486,"position":7,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"ব্যতীত","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2487,"position":8,"arabic":"عِلْمٍۢ","translation":"কোন জ্ঞান","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2488,"position":9,"arabic":"وَيَتَّبِعُ","translation":"এবং অনুসরণ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2489,"position":10,"arabic":"كُلَّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2490,"position":11,"arabic":"شَيْطَـٰنٍۢ","translation":"শয়তানকে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2491,"position":12,"arabic":"مَّرِيدٍۢ","translation":"উদ্ধত","audioUrl":"wbw/022_003_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2492,"position":13,"arabic":"٣","translation":"(৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":4,"arabic":"كُتِبَ عَلَيْهِ أَنَّهُۥ مَن تَوَلَّاهُ فَأَنَّهُۥ يُضِلُّهُۥ وَيَهْدِيهِ إِلَىٰ عَذَابِ ٱلسَّعِيرِ","translation":"about which it has been decreed that whoever entrusts himself to it, him will it lead astray and guide towards the suffering of the blazing flame!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2599.mp3","surahId":22,"words":[{"id":3953,"position":1,"arabic":"كُتِبَ","translation":"লিখে দেয়া হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3954,"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"তার সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3955,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنَّهُۥ","translation":"যে তা (এমন)","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3956,"position":4,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যে কেউ","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3957,"position":5,"arabic":"تَوَلَّاهُ","translation":"তাকে বন্ধু বানাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3958,"position":6,"arabic":"فَأَنَّهُۥ","translation":"তখন সে নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3959,"position":7,"arabic":"يُضِلُّهُۥ","translation":"তাকে বিভ্রান্ত করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3960,"position":8,"arabic":"وَيَهْدِيهِ","translation":"ও তাকে পরিচালিত করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3961,"position":9,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3962,"position":10,"arabic":"عَذَابِ","translation":"শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3963,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلسَّعِيرِ","translation":"জ্বলন্ত অাগুনের","audioUrl":"wbw/022_004_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3964,"position":12,"arabic":"٤","translation":"(৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":5,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ إِن كُنتُمْ فِى رَيْبٍۢ مِّنَ ٱلْبَعْثِ فَإِنَّا خَلَقْنَٰكُم مِّن تُرَابٍۢ ثُمَّ مِن نُّطْفَةٍۢ ثُمَّ مِنْ عَلَقَةٍۢ ثُمَّ مِن مُّضْغَةٍۢ مُّخَلَّقَةٍۢ وَغَيْرِ مُخَلَّقَةٍۢ لِّنُبَيِّنَ لَكُمْ ۚ وَنُقِرُّ فِى ٱلْأَرْحَامِ مَا نَشَآءُ إِلَىٰٓ أَجَلٍۢ مُّسَمًّۭى ثُمَّ نُخْرِجُكُمْ طِفْلًۭا ثُمَّ لِتَبْلُغُوٓا۟ أَشُدَّكُمْ ۖ وَمِنكُم مَّن يُتَوَفَّىٰ وَمِنكُم مَّن يُرَدُّ إِلَىٰٓ أَرْذَلِ ٱلْعُمُرِ لِكَيْلَا يَعْلَمَ مِنۢ بَعْدِ عِلْمٍۢ شَيْـًۭٔا ۚ وَتَرَى ٱلْأَرْضَ هَامِدَةًۭ فَإِذَآ أَنزَلْنَا عَلَيْهَا ٱلْمَآءَ ٱهْتَزَّتْ وَرَبَتْ وَأَنۢبَتَتْ مِن كُلِّ زَوْجٍۭ بَهِيجٍۢ","translation":"O MEN! If you are in doubt as to the [truth of] resurrection, [remember that,] verily, We have created [every one of] you out of dust, then out of a drop of sperm, then out of a germ-cell, then out of an embryonic lump complete [in itself] and yet incom­plete so that We might make [your origin] clear unto you. And whatever We will [to be born] We cause to rest in the [mothers’] wombs for a term set [by Us], and then We bring you forth as infants and [allow you to live] so that [some of] you might attain to maturity: for among you are such as are caused to die [in childhood], just as many a one of you is reduced in old age to a most abject state, ceasing to know anything of what he once knew so well. And [if, O man, thou art still in doubt as to resur­rection, consider this:] thou canst see the earth dry and lifeless - and [suddenly,] when We send down waters upon it, it stirs and swells and puts forth every kind of lovely plant!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2600.mp3","surahId":22,"words":[{"id":5188,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5189,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسُ","translation":"মানবজাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5190,"position":3,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5191,"position":4,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হও","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5192,"position":5,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5193,"position":6,"arabic":"رَيْبٍۢ","translation":"সন্দেহের","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5194,"position":7,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5195,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْبَعْثِ","translation":"উত্থান","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5196,"position":9,"arabic":"فَإِنَّا","translation":"তবে নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/022_005_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":5197,"position":10,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَـٰكُم","translation":"তোমাদেরকে আমরা সৃষ্টি করেছি","audioUr